    • Method Detail

      • init

        public static void init()
        Initializes the IOInterface.
        Has to be executed before run()

      • run

        public static void run()
        Runs the IOInterface.
        It does not start a new thread, so use it as your last line of code.
        To stop the Interface set running to false
        Will call IOInterface.IOListener if a registered IOInterface.Command is entered.
        Will call IOInterface.IOListener.close() if it gets closed.
